data.text:
The historians and researchers at Cape Verde History Unearthed decodes mysteries and utilizes scientific investigations, and intuitive theories to reveal and explain the hidden secrets from Cabo Verde’s past.

The researchers of CVHUnearthed fuses elements of history, and archaeology, revealing the deepest secrets of each document unearthed.

CVHUnearthed shows that the key to understanding our past is through diligent research, and without these research skills, we wouldn’t be able to unravel some of the Cabo Verde’s greatest mysteries and stories.
